    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "E. Object Sighted:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "A light emanating in the shape of a circle, of an intensity much greater",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "than that of a bright moon, giving the impression of form in connection with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "the light. The light was white in appearance and did not show any signs of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "refraction into a band or continuous spectrum. This object was traveling in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "a Northwesterly direction, 15 to 30 degrees elevation above the horizon, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "appeared to diminish considerably in size during thirty seconds of observation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "To another group, the object appeared only as a bright reflection of the sun",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
